@@ -6,7 +6,9 @@ The GNOME Build Metadata repository is where the GNOME release team manages build metadata for building the GNOME Flatpak runtime, GNOME OS, and GNOME OCI images.
 
 ## Getting started
 
-Please see [CONTRIBUTING.md](./CONTRIBUTING.md).
+If you'd like **use** GNOME OS, please see the [installation guide](https://os.gnome.org/install) on the [GNOME OS website](https://os.gnome.org/) and the [user guide](./docs/usage.md) for usage.
+
+To **contribute** to the GNOME Flatpak runtime, GNOME OS or GNOME OCI images, see [CONTRIBUTING.md](./CONTRIBUTING.md) to get started, and the [debugging guide](./docs/debugging.md) for common troubleshooting steps.
 
 ## Published build outputs
 
